
flowchart LR
    SM[SessionManager] --> MCP[MultiServerMCPClient]
    MCP --> SERVER[MCP Server]

    SM --> EH[ElicitationHandler]
    EH --> REDISMOD[RedisModule]

    REDISMOD --> STREAM[Redis Stream assist elicitation replies]
    REDISMOD --> PENDING[Redis pending elicitation keys]

    STREAM --> EH
    EH --> SM

